<div class="article-header article-header-full">
	<h1 itemprop="headline ">The Surface Book: Microsoft's Ultimate Laptop</h1>
		<div class="subtitle">Microsoft's first laptop is both versatile and powerful</div>
</div>

<div class="article-header-default row">
	<div class="col col-10 col-pc-10 col-tablet-7">


